    {
      "timestamp": "27:16",
      "ad": false,
      "speaker": "Speaker 3: Noah",
      "text": "Yeah, one example of like a different mouse behavior that we have. like inside of Figma design, if I were to like try to drag some like things inside of an auto layout container, um we have like this behavior over here where like um they'll shuffle around in real time.",
      "tone": "Explanatory, Technical"
